\v 9 Zerah, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H6440"\w* \w from|strong="H3318"\w* Ethiopia/Sudan, \w marched|strong="H3318"\w* \w with|strong="H6440"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* huge \w army|strong="H4421"\w* \w and|strong="H6440"\w* 300 chariots \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w attack|strong="H4421"\w* \add the army of Judah and Benjamin\add*. \w They|strong="H6440"\w* \w went|strong="H3318"\w* \w as|strong="H3318"\w* \w far|strong="H3318"\w* \w as|strong="H3318"\w* \add the town of\add* \w Mareshah|strong="H4762"\w* \add about 25 miles/southwest of Jerusalem\add*.  
