\c 15  
\s1 The reforms that Asa introduced  
\p
\v 1 \w The|strong="H5921"\w* \w Spirit|strong="H7307"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* God \w came|strong="H1961"\w* \w upon|strong="H5921"\w* \w Azariah|strong="H5838"\w*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Obed.  
