\p \w Jehoshaphat|strong="H3092"\w* replied, “\w King|strong="H4428"\w* Ahab, \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w should|strong="H3068"\w* \w not|strong="H3588"\w* \w say|strong="H3478"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w*!”   
