\v 14 \w When|strong="H5927"\w* \w Micaiah|strong="H4318"\w* arrived, \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \add of Israel\add* asked \w him|strong="H5414"\w*, “\w Should|strong="H4428"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w go|strong="H3212"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w attack|strong="H5927"\w* \w Ramoth|strong="H7433"\w*, \w or|strong="H3027"\w* \w not|strong="H2308"\w*?”  
\p \w Micaiah|strong="H4318"\w* replied, “Sure, \w go|strong="H3212"\w*! \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* enable \w your|strong="H5414"\w* \w army|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w defeat|strong="H5414"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w*!”   
\p
\v 15 \w But|strong="H7535"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w* Ahab \add realized that Micaiah was lying, so he\add* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* Micaiah, “\w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w told|strong="H1696"\w* \w you|strong="H5704"\w* \w many|strong="H4100"\w* \w times|strong="H6471"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H5704"\w* \w must|strong="H3808"\w* \w always|strong="H7535"\w* \w tell|strong="H1696"\w* \w only|strong="H7535"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w truth|strong="H3808"\w* \w when|strong="H5704"\w* \w you|strong="H5704"\w* \w say|strong="H1696"\w* \w what|strong="H4100"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \add has revealed to you\add*!”   
