\v 16 \w Then|strong="H7725"\w* Micaiah replied, “\add The truth is that in a vision\add* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* troops \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* \w scattered|strong="H6327"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w mountains|strong="H2022"\w*. \w They|strong="H3068"\w* \w seemed|strong="H7200"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* \w like|strong="H1004"\w* \w sheep|strong="H6629"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w did|strong="H3478"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w shepherd|strong="H7462"\w*. \w And|strong="H3478"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* said, ‘\w Their|strong="H3605"\w* master \w has|strong="H3068"\w* \w been|strong="H3808"\w* killed. \w So|strong="H3808"\w* \w tell|strong="H3605"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w go|strong="H7725"\w* \w home|strong="H1004"\w* \w peacefully|strong="H7965"\w*.’”   
\p
\v 17 Ahab said \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w Jehoshaphat|strong="H3092"\w*, “\w I|strong="H3588"\w* told \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w never|strong="H3808"\w* predicts \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w anything|strong="H3808"\w* \w good|strong="H2896"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* happen \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*! \w He|strong="H3588"\w* \add always\add* predicts \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w bad|strong="H7451"\w* \w things|strong="H7451"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* happen \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*.”   
\p
\v 18 \w But|strong="H7200"\w* Micaiah \w continued|strong="H3427"\w*, \w saying|strong="H1697"\w*, “\w Listen|strong="H8085"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w showed|strong="H7200"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w me|strong="H7200"\w*! \add In a vision\add* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w sitting|strong="H3427"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* \w throne|strong="H3678"\w*, \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w armies|strong="H6635"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8064"\w* \add standing around him\add*, \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* \w right|strong="H3225"\w* \w side|strong="H3225"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* \w left|strong="H8040"\w* \w side|strong="H3225"\w*.  
\v 19 \w And|strong="H3478"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* said, ‘\w Who|strong="H4310"\w* \w can|strong="H4310"\w* \w persuade|strong="H6601"\w* Ahab, \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w*, \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w go|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* fight \w against|strong="H5927"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* people \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w Ramoth|strong="H7433"\w*, \w in|strong="H3478"\w* order \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w may|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* \w killed|strong="H5307"\w* \w there|strong="H2088"\w*?’  
\p “Some suggested \w one|strong="H2088"\w* \w thing|strong="H2088"\w*, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* others suggested something else.   
\p
\v 20 “Finally \w one|strong="H3068"\w* \w spirit|strong="H7307"\w*, \add having received a message from Satan\add*, \w came|strong="H3318"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H3318"\w*, ‘\w I|strong="H4100"\w* \w can|strong="H4100"\w* \w do|strong="H3068"\w* \w it|strong="H6440"\w*!’  
\p “\w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w asked|strong="H4100"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w*, ‘\w How|strong="H4100"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w do|strong="H3068"\w* \w it|strong="H6440"\w*?’   
\p
\v 21 “\w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w spirit|strong="H7307"\w* replied, ‘\w I|strong="H3651"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w go|strong="H3318"\w* \w and|strong="H6213"\w* inspire \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H7307"\w* Ahab’s \w prophets|strong="H5030"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* \w tell|strong="H3605"\w* \w lies|strong="H8267"\w*.’ \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H3651"\w*, ‘\w You|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* successful; \w go|strong="H3318"\w* \w and|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w it|strong="H6213"\w*!’   
\p
\v 22 “\w So|strong="H5414"\w* \w now|strong="H6258"\w* \add I tell you that\add* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* \w caused|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w prophets|strong="H5030"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w lie|strong="H8267"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*. \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* decided \w that|strong="H3068"\w* something \w terrible|strong="H7451"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* happen \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*.”   
