\c 26  
\s1 King Uzziah of Judah  
\p
\v 1-2 After King Amaziah died, all the people of Judah appointed his son Uzziah, who then was 16 years old, as their king. \add One of the things that happened\add* while he was the king \add was that\add* his men captured Elath \add town on the Gulf of Aqaba\add* and rebuilt it.   
